data.description: The sellers received an irresistible offer they couldn’t pass up.  Thank you for your consideration.  | Prepare to be amazed by this stunningly renovated home, which is an absolute must-see! The brand-new gourmet kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line black stainless steel Bosch appliances, including a double wall oven with microwave and convection cooking. The exquisite porcelain counter features a hidden induction cooktop, providing ample counter space. The open floor plan is perfect for hosting guests, and the first-level terrace offers access to the 10th-floor courtyard.  This home features two spacious bedrooms, a den, and 2.5 bathrooms.  It has been upgraded with luxury vinyl plank flooring on all three levels and a fresh coat of paint throughout. The bathrooms on the main and second levels have been renovated to perfection. This is one of the few Silo Point condos with an in-unit storage room located off the laundry room on the second level.   The third-floor primary bedroom offers balcony access and stunning views of the water and city. The closets are spacious and feature walk-in and upgraded build-outs. Two parking spots are located in the secure resident garage convey.   This house comes with a range of luxury amenities, including a lobby, gym, and 19th-floor Sky Lounge. Don’t wait to see this one-of-a-kind home that is sure to take your breath away!   Silo Point is a modern condominium located in Locust Point. It has a rich history that makes it unique, having been originally constructed in 1923 as the largest and fastest grain elevator in the world. Today, it is an award-winning 24-story building that features bits of its history scattered throughout.   The property boasts professional on-site property management, a 24-hour front desk, a fitness center, game and conference rooms, pet areas, and a 19th-floor Sky Lounge. Its strategic location provides easy access to downtown 95, 295, 395, 695, and 895. Moreover, it is only a short distance to Fort McHenry and Tide Point, where you can take a water taxi.
